accessibility.text: The film opens to a group of friends at an open rustic steakhouse, engrossed in conversation. A waiter approaches them, carrying a tray filled with sizzling steaks. The sound and aroma of the sizzling food capture their attention, setting the scene for a delightful dining experience.
